 />\n香港而家係人為嘅地震<br />\n即使香港人死哂，香港都唔會沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港永遠會完整係到<br />\n03年開始，每次有小震動，有人會搭飛機走，我就會幫手抗震<br />\n到雨革後，香港已經震到不可逆轉。我決定搭飛機走。上到半空，望返落去，成個香港忽然好清晰<br />\n點解震，影響到啲乜野，有無得救，全部都望得一清二楚"},{"pid":"146e2329c9a8b855760c1f68a3528bdd1f886ec4","tid":1165571,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"政治本來就係損害越多人利益 先會越多人留意<br />\n<br />\n冇人係一出世就對政治有興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6d8dc9f0d3ea78dce559f8b8c59a7abcedcd1c","tid":1165571,"uid":238013,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3566a6709efd52e76492bb76f17c72ddc429b441","tid":1165571,"uid":116105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cca9ba30b49d66eb514a16fc7a57eb6bf5ab531e","tid":1165571,"uid":238013,"like":7,"dislike":110,"score":-103,"quote":{"pid":"87dcaa7ef7f7b97a99eb3b0ff49e57923d1da18b","tid":1165571,"uid":37600,"like":250,"dislike":10,"score":240,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"咁你去死啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"死又何妨？<br />\n<br />\n講到自己永生咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"佢叫你依家死呀賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"我早啲死，對件有幫助咩？<br />\n(同你去遊行嘅效果一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"ce1f8e9a7cae2697e506780c16a99b1eab7e465d","tid":1165571,"uid":47160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"人地就覺醒，你就變矇撚"},{"pid":"a9686e703ac9e3589c9b525c86d7744af0de79cb","tid":1165571,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三毛又開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散播失敗主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><